Package com.da.antiphish.lists

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlacklistEntry
    BlacklistEntry represents an entry of the phishing blacklist from PhishTank and includes the following information: id: the phish_id field from a PhishTank entry url: the url of the phishing website
    ContentlistEntry
    ContentlistEntry represents an entry of the phishing content list and includes the following information: id: the id of the entry text: the text (keyword or phrase) lang: the language of the text confidence: the confidence of the text
    ListsHandler
    ListsHandler is responsible for maintaining all lists/maps.
    MetalistEntry
    MetalistEntry represents an entry of the phishing meta list and includes the following information: id: the id of the entry content: the suspicious content (keyword or phrase) confidence: the confidence of the content
    ScriptlistEntry
    ScriptlistEntry represents an entry of the suspicious scripting content list and includes the following information: id: the id of the entry content: the suspicious content (command) confidence: the confidence of the content
    WhitelistEntry
    WhitelistEntry represents an entry of the whitelist and includes the following information: id: the id of the entry url: the url of the website
